1. make a main folder
2. in terminal run npm init
3. make index.js is main file
4. in package.json -> edit script => "start":"node index.js" => then in terminal run npm start 
5. npm i express
6. make a express app  
7. npm i dotenv
8. require('dotenv').config() => to use .env variables in app code
9. define variable in .env file
10. use .env variable in app code => process.env.var_name in app code 